# CLAUDE.md — justec-public-api

## What This Is

The **Public Persona API** — a Node.js/TypeScript middleware that powers the Justec Virtual Front Desk on surfstyk.com. It sits between the chat frontend and LLM providers, handling session management, qualification scoring, model routing, tool integration, and security.

This is NOT an OpenClaw agent. It's a standalone HTTP service.

